{"tid":1992797,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【警察街頭無故擄走記者–壹週刊譴責聲明】","createTime":"2020-04-28T10:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T11:13:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9568fc6d0b83dbe4edb72c193fa3f3e70ba50015","tid":1992797,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"【警察街頭無故擄走記者&ndash;壹週刊譴責聲明】<br />\n<br />\n本刊記者於下午四時半，在清水灣採訪並拍攝涉及助理警務處長陶輝相關的調查新聞，當完成採訪工作離開，突然遭警方在公眾地方無理拘捕，並扣押記者到將軍澳警署。記者已向在場警務人員表明身分。<br />\n<br />\n《壹週刊》嚴厲譴責警察濫用公權力，恐嚇記者，以圖阻礙《壹週刊》記者調查及揭發警隊高層醜聞。<br />\n不怕權貴，敢於揭露真相，這正正是《壹週刊》編輯部的宗旨。<br />\n<br />\n《壹週刊》編輯部<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd0913054dcdbc37667a361cb9c8ce795096ad2","tid":1992797,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"警隊高層醜聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"}]}